name: PewPewPew
description:
Instead of waiting for a shooting star to grant your wish, use the PewPewPew to summon a shooting star right in your back yard! Not only does it summon a shooting star, it summons a special kind of shooting star. 

these special stars gives:
1. a chance to rewrite or choose your destiny. You can also intertwine your destiny with a specific person in mind (Special stars with this ability only comes when you truly need it)
2. a burst of good luck for the day
3. Attracts other shooting stars for a mini star show performance
4. Fulfill your current needs for one day

The PewPewPew now comes in different colors. come get yours now at 1-800-Pews

Have a Pewtiful day
